ter Summersisle\n|\n|-\n| ''{{sortname|The|Elephant King}}''\n| Diana Hunt\n|\n|-\n| ''30 Days''\n| Maura\n|\n|-\n| 2007\n| ''{{sortname|The|Stone Angel|dab=2007 film}}''\n| Hagar Shipley\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2008\n| ''[[Lovely, Still]]''\n| Mary\n|\n|-\n| ''[[W. (film)|W.]]''\n| [[Barbara Bush]]\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"4\" | 2009\n| ''{{sortname|The|Velveteen Rabbit}}''\n| Swan\n| Voice role\n|-\n| ''[[According to Greta]]''\n| Katherine\n|\n|-\n| ''[[PoliWood (film)|PoliWood]]''\n| Herself\n| Documentary\n|-\n| ''[[The Loss of a Teardrop Diamond]]''\n| Miss Adie\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2010\n| ''{{sortname|The|Mighty Macs|dab=film}}''\n| Mother St. John\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Main Street (2010 film)|Main Street]]''\n| Georgiana Carr\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2011\n| ''[[Another Happy Day]]''\n| Doris\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Someday This Pain Will Be Useful to You (film)|Someday This Pain Will Be Useful to You]]''\n| Nanette\n|\n|-\n| 2013\n| ''[[Wish You Well (film)|Wish You Well]]''\n| Louisa Mae Cardinal\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"5\" | 2014\n| ''[[Two Men in Town (2014 film)|Two Men in Town]]''\n| Garnett's mother\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Draft Day]]''\n| Barb Weaver\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Flowers in the Attic]]''\n| Olivia Foxworth\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Interstellar (film)|Interstellar]]''\n| Old Murph\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Petals on the Wind]]''\n| Olivia Foxworth\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"3\" | 2015\n| ''[[The Age of Adaline]]''\n| Flemming\n| \n|-\n| ''[[Unity (film)|Unity]]''\n| Narrator\n| Documentary\n|-\n| ''[[About Scout]]''\n| Gram\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2016\n| ''[[Wiener-Dog (film)|Wiener-Dog]]''\n| Nana\n|\n|-\n| ''[[Custody (2016 film)|Custody]]''\n| Beatrice Fisher\n| \n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2017\n| ''[[The House of Tomorrow (2017 film)|The House of Tomorrow]]''\n| Josephine Prendergast\n| Also executive producer\n|-\n| ''[[All I Wish]]''\n| Celia Berges\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" | 2018\n| ''[[Nostalgia (2018 film)|Nostalgia]]''\n| Helen Greer\n|\n|-\n| ''[[The Tale]]''\n| Nettie\n|\n|-\n| rowspan=\"2\" |